descp2: bool, if `False`, will pad dimensions with unknown size to maximum length in batch. If `True`, will pad dimensions with unknown size to bucket boundary minus 1 (i.e., the maximum length in each bucket), and caller must ensure that the source `Dataset` does not contain any elements with length longer than `max(bucket_boundaries)`.
